details.name: Shuriken Toss
details.description: Hurls a deadly shuriken at an enemy unit, dealing damage and mini-stunning the target.  The shuriken will bounce between any Tracked units who are within a 1200 radius of each other. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Allows Shuriken Toss to bounce twice on each hero.
